Prepare for an adrenaline-fueled battle of wits in Imposter Smasher – the ultimate test of deception and strategy! As a vigilant crewmate, your mission is to identify and eliminate the imposters lurking among you before it's too late.

Navigate through intricate mazes, complete tasks, and keep a keen eye out for any suspicious behavior. But beware – the imposters will stop at nothing to sabotage your efforts and eliminate the crew. Use your deductive skills to uncover their true identities and vote them out before they strike.
